Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with text-based systems and keyword extraction, which are common topics in natural language processing.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a likely category as keyword extraction is used for efficient document retrieval.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the proposed method uses unsupervised learning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems that can summarize and visualize documents.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possible category as the proposed method uses graph-theoretic measures applied to graphs derived from text.
